base_url <- "https://gegevensmagazijn.tweedekamer.nl/OData/v4/2.0/"
entity <- "Zaak"
filter1 <- "?$filter=Verwijderd eq false"
filter2 <- " and Soort eq 'Motie'"
filter3 <- " and contains(Onderwerp, 'dier')"
expand <- "&$expand=Besluit($expand=Stemming)"

url <- paste0(base_url, entity, filter1, filter2, filter3, expand)
url <- str_replace_all(url, " ", "%20")

result <- read_json(url)

result$value

```{r}
#| label: setup

# Load packages
library(tidyverse)
library(jsonlite)

base_url <- "https://gegevensmagazijn.tweedekamer.nl/OData/v4/2.0/"
entity <- "Zaak"
filter1 <- "?$filter=Verwijderd eq false"
filter2 <- " and Soort eq 'Motie'"
filter3 <- " and contains(Onderwerp, 'dier')"
expand <- "&$expand=Besluit($expand=Stemming)"

url <- paste0(base_url, entity, filter1, filter2, filter3, expand)
url <- str_replace_all(url, " ", "%20")

result <- read_json(url)

result$value

example_zaak <- result$value[[1]]

clean_zaak <- function(zaak) {
  tibble(
    id = zaak$Id,
    title = zaak$Titel,
    subject = zaak$Onderwerp,
    start_date = zaak$GestartOp
  )
}

df <- map_df(result$value, clean_zaak)

clean_besluit <- function(zaak) {
  tibble(
    id = zaak$Id,
    title = zaak$Titel,
    subject = zaak$Onderwerp,
    start_date = zaak$GestartOp
  )
}
```
